11
00:01:56,000 --> 00:01:56,600
Bed 07.

12
00:01:57,320 --> 00:01:57,880
What's going on?

13
00:01:58,160 --> 00:01:59,190
Fire in the house from an old appliance.

14
00:01:59,440 --> 00:02:00,270
A guy was trapped in the fire.

15
00:02:00,360 --> 00:02:01,390
His brother ran back to save him

16
00:02:01,520 --> 00:02:02,270
and was badly burned.

17
00:02:02,390 --> 00:02:03,270
The two were on the second floor.

18
00:02:03,270 --> 00:02:04,270
When they jumped down,

19
00:02:04,470 --> 00:02:05,750
the younger brother
hit his backside on a metal frame.

20
00:02:09,790 --> 00:02:10,600
The thoracic drainage bottle first.

21
00:02:10,630 --> 00:02:11,070
OK.

22
00:02:18,120 --> 00:02:19,470
Notify the burn unit to open the trachea

23
00:02:19,510 --> 00:02:20,280
and surgical system

24
00:02:20,280 --> 00:02:21,070
for a hospital-wide consultation. Now.

25
00:02:21,070 --> 00:02:21,470
Got it.

