of the body,

668
00:30:31,340 --> 00:30:32,230
mainly in the duodenum.

669
00:30:32,450 --> 00:30:33,260
It can cause symptoms
such as abdominal pain,

670
00:30:33,340 --> 00:30:34,580
diarrhea, and indigestion

671
00:30:34,690 --> 00:30:35,470
and lead to Giardiasis.

672
00:30:35,690 --> 00:30:36,500
In the last decade,

673
00:30:36,580 --> 00:30:37,630
due to the growth
of the tourism industry,

674
00:30:37,690 --> 00:30:39,230
it has become more prevalent
among travelers,

675
00:30:39,290 --> 00:30:40,630
so it is also called
traveler's diarrhea.

676
00:30:42,380 --> 00:30:43,870
The intestinal capsule endoscopy?

